    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm honestly so sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014it's basically been pampered since day one! It looks and drives like it just rolled off the lot. If you're looking for something that's been loved and kept in pristine condition, this is definitely the one for you. Let's get you behind the wheel for a test drive!",
