      "timestep_posted": 24
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a total dream on wheels? I'm parting with my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, she\u2019s in such incredible shape you\u2019d swear she just rolled off the showroom floor! This car has been pampered since day one\u2014no scratches, a spotless interior, and that fresh-car feel that\u2019s so hard to find. It drives like a dream and looks even better in person. I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and I\u2019m looking for someone who will love it just as much as I have. Come take a look and see for yourself\u2014you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
