      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 24
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3 in impeccable condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and high-pressure Double VANOS. The drivetrain is mated to a crisp 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-variable differential lock. Mechanically, this vehicle is peerless: the rod bearing service is documented, the VANOS system has been overhauled with uprated components, and the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced. Suspension geometry remains true with fresh bushings and factory-spec dampers. The exterior retains its factory depth and gloss, while the interior shows zero bolster wear or pixel degradation. A turn-key specimen for the discerning collector.",
